data.name: tbxLoad.Text
data.value: 1. Press Load and choose a text file within the input file. 2. Press Process to begin execution of statistical analysis suite. 3. Choose an option to generate lotto numbers. 4. Choose the amount of tickets you want it to generate. 5. Generate the numbers, and good luck!

data.name: tbxTickets.Text
data.value: Numbers generated will be printed here. The numbers you load must correspond to the type of game you're playing, as analysis will differ between games (i.e. Fantasy 5 numbers require a 5 number format, Powerball numbers requite a 7 number format, etc.)
